Prompt Chain Document
Project: I Asked ChatGPT to Run My Day – Here’s What Happened

Prompt 1: Topic & Angle Definition
Prompt:
You are a content strategist.
Analyze the idea “I asked ChatGPT to run my day.”
Suggest the best storytelling angle, target audience, and value proposition
for a YouTube video.

Purpose:
 To define the core idea, audience relevance, and narrative angle.

Prompt 2: YouTube Title Generation
Prompt:
Generate 10 catchy, non-clickbait YouTube titles
for a video where I let ChatGPT control my entire day.
Tone should be personal, productivity-focused, and modern.

Purpose:
 To generate engaging titles optimized for curiosity and click-through rate.

Prompt 3: Title Selection
Prompt:
From the generated titles, select the most effective one
and explain briefly why it works.

Final Selected Title:
 I Asked ChatGPT to Run My Day – Here’s What Happened
Purpose:
 To finalize the strongest title for audience engagement.

Prompt 4: Video Hook
Prompt:
Write a compelling 10–15 second YouTube hook
for a video where I let ChatGPT plan my entire day.
Make it sound natural and human.

Purpose:
 To capture viewer attention in the first few seconds.

Prompt 5: Full Video Script
Prompt:
Write a full YouTube video script (5–7 minutes)
about following ChatGPT’s instructions for an entire day.

Structure:
- Hook
- Introduction
- Morning routine
- Workday experience
- Challenges
- Results
- Honest reflection
- Call to action

Tone: conversational and realistic.

Purpose:
 To generate a complete, ready-to-use video script.

Prompt 6: Thumbnail Concept
Prompt:
Act as a YouTube thumbnail designer.
Create a high-conversion thumbnail concept
including text, visual layout, and emotional focus
for the video “I Asked ChatGPT to Run My Day – Here’s What Happened”.

Purpose:
 To design a visually compelling thumbnail for higher CTR.

Prompt 7: AI Image Generation Prompt
Prompt:
Write a detailed AI image generation prompt
for creating a YouTube thumbnail.
Style should be modern, high contrast, expressive,
and optimized for YouTube.

Purpose:
 To generate the thumbnail image using AI tools.

Prompt 8: Video Creation Workflow
Prompt:
Suggest a simple workflow using free tools
to convert a YouTube script into a complete video.

Purpose:
 To document how the script is turned into a final video.

Prompt 9: Reflection & Learnings
Prompt:
Write a short reflection explaining what this experiment shows
about using AI for productivity and content creation,
including benefits and limitations.

Purpose:
 To conclude the project with insights and learning outcomes.


